org.gvsig.gpe.kml.parser.v21.geometries
Class RegionBinding

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.gpe.kml.parser.v21.geometries.RegionBinding

public class RegionBinding
extends java.lang.Object

This class parses a Region Kml tag. Example: 

  
 <Region>
 <LatLonAltBox>
 <north>43.374</north>
 <south>42.983</south>
 <east>-0.335</east>
 <west>-1.423</west>
 <rotation>39.37878630116985</rotation>
 </LatLonAltBox>
 </Region>

Author:
Jorge Piera LLodrá (jorge.piera@iver.es)
See Also:
http://code.google.com/apis/kml/documentation/kml_tags_21.html#region
